caption:

1. Pay attention to the Bicycles *and* its Pedals
2. Sacrifice to the Bars *and* its Pool Tables
3. Gain Knowledge via Surfing Net
4. Take Stand when Making Better World
5. Understand you gotta Tying Shoelace if you want Knots
